 The standalone Lookup application now uses a dedicated purple BWT favicon across all pages.
 
-- The browser icon uses a high-contrast white BWT mark on a purple background.
+- The browser icon uses a smooth vector-style white BWT mark on a purple background with rounded corners optimized for favicon rendering.
 - The shared site head publishes the favicon consistently on login, Lookup, Duplicates, Sources, and Metrics pages.
 - The browser theme color is set to the same purple family for supported mobile and installed-browser surfaces.
 - The favicon is stored under `app/public/favicon.svg` and is included automatically in the application image during the normal app rebuild.
